24},"img",{"alt":222,"src":223},"Screenshot of code showing CSS variables ","/img/articles/css-vars.png",[],{"type":24,"tag":48,"props":226,"children":228},{"id":227},"_4-calculations-are-here-and-they-work-beautifully",[229],{"type":29,"value":230},"4. Calculations are here and they work beautifully.",{"type":24,"tag":25,"props":232,"children":233},{},[234,236,242],{"type":29,"value":235},"With ",{"type":24,"tag":101,"props":237,"children":239},{"className":238},[],[240],{"type":29,"value":241},"calc",{"type":29,"value":243}," you can do much more then you ever could before. It allows you to add, subtract, multiply, and divide in CSS. You can even do calculation using different data types such as percents and pixels.",{"type":24,"tag":94,"props":245,"children":247},{"className":96,"code":246,"language":98,"meta":7,"style":7},"width: calc(100% - 30px);\n",[248],{"type":24,"tag":101,"props":249,"children":250},{"__ignoreMap":7},[251],{"type":24,"tag":105,"props":252,"children":253},{"class":107,"line":108},[254],{"type":24,"tag":105,"props":255,"children":256},{},[257],{"type":29,"value":246},{"type":24,"tag":48,"props":259,"children":261},{"id":260},"_5-flexbox-and-css-grid-have-changed-the-game",[262],{"type":29,"value":263},"5. Flexbox and CSS grid have changed the game",{"type":24,"tag":25,"props":265,"children":266},{},[267],{"type":29,"value":268},"Flexbox and CSS Grid have made designing for the web an absolute treat.  A basic bootstrap grid system can be created with a few lines of code. You no longer need to use a framework to create a responsive website.",{"type":24,"tag":48,"props":270,"children":272},{"id":271},"_6-its-the-standard-to-style-the-web",[273],{"type":29,"value":274},"6. It’s the standard to style the web.",{"type":24,"tag":25,"props":276,"children":277},{},[278],{"type":29,"value":279},"The fundamentals of writing CSS syntax hasn’t changed much. You can rest assured that if you learn CSS, you will always know how to style the web. CSS has ove